metadata.name: Princess of the Sea, Amphitrite
metadata.description:
''This world made me who I am,
Then reminded me who I was.
This world lied to me and said,
I love you more than he does.

I threw myself into the sea,
and felt the waves soothing my soul.
This is when I knew I found my peace,
In the Ocean is where I belong.''

- Princess of the Sea, Amphitrite
